title: Boxing with Chris Mannix - Canelo Alvarez stops by
itunes:title: Boxing with Chris Mannix - Canelo Alvarez stops by
description:
Boxing Insider for ESPN, Mike Coppinger stops by the podcast to talk with Chris about the Tyson Fury-Dillion Whyte fight and what might be next for Fury. Later, Canelo Alvarez joins the program to talk about his upcoming fight with Dmitry Bivol and if we will see him get in the ring again with GGG. #Herd
